
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "AdoptiiCainiPui";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<html>
<head>
    <title>Heaven</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style1.css">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js">
    </script>







    <style>
        body {
            background-color: lightblue;
            background-size: cover;
        }


        .center {
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            width: 50%;
        }



        .images {
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .no-padding .col-md-6 {
            padding: 0;
        }

        h3.heading {
            margin-top: 100px;
            text-align: auto;
            font-size: 1.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1.9rem;
        }



        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: auto auto auto auto auto auto;
            grid-gap: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            padding-right: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

            .container .box {
                position: relative;
                width: 260px;
                margin-right: 40px;
                background: #7FFFD4;
                padding: 20px 40px 40px;
                text-align: center;
                overflow: hidden;
                border-radius: 20px;
            }

                .container .box:nth-child(1) {
                    background: linear-gradient(45deg,#036eb7,#64eaff);
                }

                .container .box:nth-child(2) {
                    background: linear-gradient(45deg,#E91E63,#ed55ff);
                }

                .container .box:nth-child(3) {
                    background: linear-gradient(45deg,#086d35,#00ff72);
                }

                .container .box:nth-child(4) {
                    background: linear-gradient(45deg,#f05a4f,#f4c030);
                }

                .container .box:nth-child(5) {
                    background: linear-gradient(45deg,#036eb7,#64eaff);
                }




                .container .box h3 {
                    position: relative;
                    margin: 0;
                    padding: 0;
                    font-size: 40px;
                    color: black;
                    z-index: 1;
                    opacity: 0.4;
                }


                .container .box p {
                    position: relative;
                    margin: 0;
                    padding: 0;
                    font-size: 40px;
                    color: black;
                    z-index: 1;
                    opacity: 0.4;
                }

        .card {
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            width: 50%;
        }

        .btn {
            border-width: medium;
            background-color: black;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-transform: capitalize;
            padding: .5rem 1.1rem;
            font-size: .9rem;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>

    <div class="container-fluid padding">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
            <h3 class="heading">Adoptii caini pui</h3>
            <div class="heading-underline"></div>
        </div>


        <div class="row no-padding">

            <div class="col-md-6"> 
                <a href="">
                    <img class="images" src="~/images/p33.jpg">
                </a>
                <p>
                    Micutul Oscar este o minune pe care am salvat-o recent de pe campuri. <br>
                    A fost deparazitat intern si extern si a inceput schema de vaccinare.
                    Este usor timid dar in preajma oamenilor, cu atentie si rabdare oferite cu siguranta va deveni un alt catelus.
                    La maturitate va fi de talie medie.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img class="images" src="~/images/1.jpg">
                <p>Jessie are aproape 4 luni, este dulce si iubitoare, jucausa si haioasa si are nevoie de o familie. <br> La maturitate va avea in jur de 5 kg </p>

            </div>





        </div>   <!---End Row-->
    </div>   <!---End Jumbotron-->
    </div>
</body>
</html>